# Heritage Oak Dental — environment variables
#
# This project is a fully static React + Vite site.
# No environment variables are required for production.
#
# If you add a backend API in the future, add it here and reference it as:
#   VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.vercel.app
#
# All Vite client-side env vars must be prefixed with VITE_
# and accessed via: import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL
